                </p>
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <p>
Defined and continuous on the interval <m>[-10,10]</m>.
                        </p>
                    </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
The slope tangent to the graph of <m>f(x)</m> at <m>x=4</m> is positive
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
<m>f'(x)&lt;0</m> at <m>x=8</m>
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
<m>\lim_{h\to 0} \frac{f( 0 +h)-f( 0 )}{h}</m> does not exist
                            </p>
                        </li>
                        <li>
                            <p>
The rate of change of <m>f(x)</m> when <m>x=-2</m> is zero
                            </p>
                        </li>
                </ul>
            </li>
